tflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#05070d\"/><title>Matias Nature — Reservas diretas +25% com E-commerce &amp; App PWA | Element Group</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Como a Element Group eliminou a dependência de OTAs e aumentou as reservas diretas da Matias Nature em 25% com e-commerce, app PWA e social media. PageSpeed 96.\"/><meta name=\"application-name\" content=\"Element Group\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.json\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-image-preview:large\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://elementgroup.pt/portfolio/matias-nature-portugal\"/><meta name=\"mobile-web-app-capable\" content=\"yes\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-title\" content=\"Element Group\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style\" content=\"default\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Matias Nature — Reservas diretas +25% com E-commerce &amp; App PWA | Element Group\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Como a Element Group eliminou a dependência de OTAs e aumentou as reservas diretas da Matias Nature em 25% com e-commerce, app PWA e social media. PageSpeed 96.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://elementgroup.pt/portfolio/matias-nature-portugal\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://elementgroup.pt/images/MNSITE.webp\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Matias Nature — Reservas diretas +25% com E-commerce &amp; App PWA | Element Group\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Como a Element Group eliminou a dependência de OTAs e aumentou as reservas diretas da Matias Nature em 25% com e-commerce, app PWA e social media. PageSpeed 96.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://elementgroup.pt/images/MNSITE.webp\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/x-icon\" sizes=\"48x48\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon0.svg?3b8331f96fba45c7\" type=\"image/svg+xml\" sizes=\"any\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon1.png?2dccf3bf3254d5b8\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"96x96\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-icon.png?903b574816cb18b2\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"180x180\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"nav-wrap\"><nav class=\"nav\"><a class=\"brand\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Element Group Digital Solutions — Início\"><div class=\"mark\">E</div><div class=\"name\"><b>Element Group</b><small>Digital Solutions</small></div></a><nav class=\"nav-links\" aria-label=\"Navegação principal\"><a href=\"/servicos\" class=\"nav-link\"><span class=\"nav-link-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 2 2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5\"></path></svg></span>Serviços</a><a href=\"/portfolio\" class=\"nav-link nav-link--active\" aria-current=\"page\"><span class=\"nav-link-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"></rect><rect x=\"14\" y=\"3\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"></rect><rect x=\"3\" y=\"14\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"></rect><rect x=\"14\" y=\"14\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"></rect></svg></span>Portfolio</a><a href=\"/blog\" class=\"nav-link\"><span class=\"nav-link-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 20h9M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4Z\"></path></svg></span>Blog</a><a href=\"/sobre\" class=\"nav-link\"><span class=\"nav-link-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M4 20c0-4 3.582-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\"></path></svg></span>Sobre</a><a href=\"/recursos\" class=\"nav-link\"><span class=\"nav-link-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v6h6M8 13h8M8 17h5\"></path></svg></span>Recursos</a><a href=\"/parcerias\" class=\"nav-link\"><span class=\"nav-link-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></span>Parcerias</a><a href=\"/contacto\" class=\"nav-link\"><span class=\"nav-link-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg></span>Contacto</a></nav><div class=\"nav-cta\"><a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"/contacto\"><span>Pedir orçamento</span><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><button class=\"menu-btn\" aria-label=\"Abrir menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 12h18M3 6h18M3 18h18\"></path></svg></button></div></nav></div><main><div class=\"cs-page\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Início\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Portfólio\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/portfolio\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Matias Nature\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/portfolio/matias-nature-portugal\"}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Matias Nature — E-commerce + App PWA\",\"description\":\"Como a Element Group eliminou a dependência de OTAs e aumentou as reservas diretas da Matias Nature em 25% com e-commerce, app PWA e social media. PageSpeed 96.\",\"image\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/images/MNSITE.webp\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Element Group\",\"url\":\"https://elementgroup.pt\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Element Group\",\"url\":\"https://elementgroup.pt\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/logo.png\"}},\"datePublished\":\"2025-01-01\",\"dateModified\":\"2025-06-01\",\"about\":{\"@type\":\"Thing\",\"name\":\"Matias Nature\"},\"review\":{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"reviewBody\":\"Desde o primeiro contato até a entrega foi excecional! A equipa entendeu exatamente o que precisávamos e entregou uma plataforma que já está a gerar resultados reais.\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Cliente Matias Nature\"},\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":\"5\",\"bestRating\":\"5\"}}}</script><nav class=\"cs-breadcrumb\" aria-label=\"Navegação de migalhas\"><a href=\"/\">Início</a><span aria-hidden=\"true\">›</span><a href=\"/portfolio\">Portfólio</a><span aria-hidden=\"true\">›</span><span aria-current=\"page\">Matias Nature</span></nav><header class=\"cs-hero\"><div class=\"cs-hero-img\"><img src=\"/images/MNSITE.webp\" alt=\"De plataformas terceiras a reservas 100% diretas.\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\"/></div><div class=\"cs-hero-overlay\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"cs-hero-inner\"><div class=\"cs-hero-tags\"><span class=\"cs-tag\">E-commerce</span><span class=\"cs-tag cs-tag--year\">2025</span></div><h1 class=\"cs-hero-title\">De plataformas terceiras a reservas 100% diretas.</h1><p class=\"cs-hero-sub\">A Matias Nature pagava 15-20% de comissão por cada reserva. Criámos uma plataforma digital própria que coloca o controlo — e o dinheiro — nas mãos do cliente.</p><div class=\"cs-hero-results\" aria-label=\"Resultados principais\"><div class=\"cs-hero-result\"><span class=\"cs-hero-result-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 19V5M5 12l7-7 7 7\"></path></svg></span><div><span class=\"cs-hero-result-val\">+25%</span><span class=\"cs-hero-result-label\">Reservas diretas em 90 dias</span></div></div><div class=\"cs-hero-result\"><span class=\"cs-hero-result-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z\"></path></svg></span><div><span class=\"cs-hero-result-val\">PageSpeed 96</span><span class=\"cs-hero-result-label\">Performance desktop</span></div></div><div class=\"cs-hero-result\"><span class=\"cs-hero-result-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 19V5M5 12l7-7 7 7\"></path></svg></span><div><span class=\"cs-hero-result-val\">+30%</span><span class=\"cs-hero-result-label\">Retorno de clientes via app</span></div></div></div></div></header><div class=\"cs-context\"><div class=\"cs-context-inner\"><div class=\"cs-context-item\"><span class=\"cs-context-label\">Cliente</span><span class=\"cs-context-val\">Matias Nature</span></div><div class=\"cs-context-item\"><span class=\"cs-context-label\">Categoria</span><span class=\"cs-context-val\">E-commerce</span></div><div class=\"cs-context-item\"><span class=\"cs-context-label\">Ano</span><span class=\"cs-context-val\">2025</span></div><div class=\"cs-context-item\"><span class=\"cs-context-label\">Entregáveis</span><span class=\"cs-context-val cs-context-pills\"><span class=\"cs-pill\">Website E-commerce</span><span class=\"cs-pill\">App PWA</span><span class=\"cs-pill\">Social Media</span></span></div><a href=\"https://www.matiasnature.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"cs-live-btn\"><span class=\"cs-live-dot\"></span>Ver site<svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"cs-body\"><section class=\"cs-section\" aria-labelledby=\"cs-challenge-title\"><div class=\"cs-section-inner\"><div class=\"cs-section-label\"><span class=\"cs-step\">01</span><span>Desafio</span></div><div class=\"cs-section-content\"><h2 id=\"cs-challenge-title\" class=\"cs-section-title\">O problema: margens comidas por comissões</h2><p class=\"cs-body-text\">A Matias Nature dependia exclusivamente de plataformas OTA — Booking, Airbnb, Tripadvisor — para conseguir reservas. Cada reserva custava entre 15% e 20% de comissão, reduzindo drasticamente a margem de lucro.</p><p class=\"cs-body-text\">Não havia website próprio, não havia app, não havia nenhuma forma de comunicar diretamente com os clientes existentes para promover regresso. O negócio estava refém de algoritmos alheios.</p><p class=\"cs-body-text\">A necessidade era clara: criar uma presença digital autónoma que permitisse reservas diretas, fidelização de clientes e independência das plataformas de terceiros.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"cs-section cs-section--alt\" aria-labelledby=\"cs-solution-title\"><div class=\"cs-section-inner\"><div class=\"cs-section-label\"><span class=\"cs-step\">02</span><span>Solução</span></div><div class=\"cs-section-content\"><h2 id=\"cs-solution-title\" class=\"cs-section-title\">A solução: ecossistema digital completo</h2><p class=\"cs-body-text\">Desenvolvemos um website e-commerce com sistema de reservas integrado e checkout nativo — sem intermediários, sem comissões. O fluxo de reserva foi otimizado para conversão mobile-first, com menos de 3 cliques da landing page ao pagamento confirmado.</p><p class=\"cs-body-text\">A App PWA (Progressive Web App) permite aos clientes anteriores aceder a ofertas exclusivas, repetir reservas e receber notificações push — um canal de marketing direto com 0% de comissão e altíssima taxa de engagement.</p><p class=\"cs-body-text\">A estratégia de social media foi alinhada com o funil de conversão, direcionando tráfego diretamente para o website próprio em vez de para as plataformas OTA.</p><ul class=\"cs-highlights\" aria-label=\"Destaques da solução\"><li class=\"cs-highlight-item\"><span class=\"cs-highlight-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span>Sistema de reservas sem comissões</li><li class=\"cs-highlight-item\"><span class=\"cs-highlight-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span>App PWA com notificações push</li><li class=\"cs-highlight-item\"><span class=\"cs-highlight-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span>Checkout em 3 cliques</li><li class=\"cs-highlight-item\"><span class=\"cs-highlight-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span>Integração com pagamentos portugueses</li><li class=\"cs-highlight-item\"><span class=\"cs-highlight-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span>SEO técnico para turismo local</li><li class=\"cs-highlight-item\"><span class=\"cs-highlight-icon\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span>Social media orientado à conversão</li></ul></div></div></section><section class=\"cs-section\" aria-labelledby=\"cs-results-title\"><div class=\"cs-section-inner\"><div class=\"cs-section-label\"><span class=\"cs-step\">03</span><span>Resultados</span></div><div class=\"cs-section-content\"><h2 id=\"cs-results-title\" class=\"cs-section-title\">Resultados em 90 dias</h2><div class=\"cs-result-grid\" aria-label=\"Métricas de resultado\"><div class=\"cs-result-card\"><span class=\"cs-result-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 19V5M5 12l7-7 7 7\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"cs-result-val\">+25%</span><span class=\"cs-result-label\">Reservas diretas no primeiro trimestre</span></div><div class=\"cs-result-card\"><span class=\"cs-result-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"cs-result-val\">96</span><span class=\"cs-result-label\">PageSpeed desktop (máximo 100)</span></div><div class=\"cs-result-card\"><span class=\"cs-result-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 19V5M5 12l7-7 7 7\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"cs-result-val\">+30%</span><span class=\"cs-result-label\">Taxa de retorno via App PWA</span></div><div class=\"cs-result-card\"><span class=\"cs-result-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span><span class=\"cs-result-val\">0%</span><span class=\"cs-result-label\">Comissão paga nas reservas diretas</span></div><div class=\"cs-result-card\"><span class=\"cs-result-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"cs-result-val\">&lt;2s</span><span class=\"cs-result-label\">Tempo de carregamento da página</span></div></div><p class=\"cs-body-text cs-results-note\">Em 90 dias após o lançamento, a Matias Nature registou um crescimento significativo nas reservas diretas e uma redução efetiva da dependência das plataformas OTA — traduzindo-se diretamente em maior margem por reserva.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"cs-testimonial-wrap\" aria-label=\"Testemunho do cliente\"><div class=\"cs-testimonial\"><div class=\"cs-testimonial-quotes\" aria-hidden=\"true\">“</div><blockquote class=\"cs-testimonial-text\">Desde o primeiro contato até a entrega foi excecional! A equipa entendeu exatamente o que precisávamos e entregou uma plataforma que já está a gerar resultados reais.</blockquote><footer class=\"cs-testimonial-footer\"><div class=\"cs-testimonial-stars\" aria-label=\"5 estrelas\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5 2 7.5L12 17l-6.5 4 2-7.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5 2 7.5L12 17l-6.5 4 2-7.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5 2 7.5L12 17l-6.5 4 2-7.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5 2 7.5L12 17l-6.5 4 2-7.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5 2 7.5L12 17l-6.5 4 2-7.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg></div><div><span class=\"cs-testimonial-author\">Cliente Matias Nature</span><span class=\"cs-testimonial-role\">Proprietário</span></div></footer></div></section></div><nav class=\"cs-nav-projects\" aria-label=\"Navegar entre projetos\"><div class=\"cs-nav-projects-inner\"><a class=\"cs-nav-project cs-nav-project--prev\" href=\"/portfolio/football-nation-store-branding\"><span class=\"cs-nav-direction\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7\"></path></svg>Projeto anterior</span><span class=\"cs-nav-client\">Football Nation Store</span></a><a class=\"cs-nav-all\" href=\"/portfolio\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"></rect><rect x=\"14\" y=\"3\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"></rect><rect x=\"3\" y=\"14\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"></rect><rect x=\"14\" y=\"14\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"></rect></svg>Ver portfólio</a><a class=\"cs-nav-project cs-nav